title: Lessons from the Brian Rose Implosion, with Nic Gabriel & Coffeezilla
description:
What have we learnt from Brian Rose's spectacular London Mayor flameout, and assorted other scams? This was a conversation including Nic Gabriel, the original co-host of London Real, Coffeezilla, who has done so much to expose Brian over the last months, hosted by Rebel Wisdom in the Digital Campfire.

David Fuller has just written a new Medium piece summarising the unanswered questions about Brian's mayoral bid, in particular, whether any of the money from the 'Digital Freedom Platform' scam was used to fund it. Brian is threatening to sue anyone who makes that claim, by the way: https://medium.com/rebel-wisdom/did-brian-rose-use-the-money-he-scammed-from-his-followers-to-run-for-mayor-bb317cf68ddb

Check out the interview where Nic Gabriel broke his silence on Brian Rose & London Real: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6hOQCUj3wyY&t=2267s

Nic's 'Liberation Mentor' podcast: https://www.liberationmentor.com/

Coffeezilla's channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCFQMnBA3CS502aghlcr0_aw

And check out the upcoming conversations in the Digital Campfire here: https://rebelwisdom.co.uk/campfire-events
